<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1482314-what-makes-beautiful-exiles-a-novel-when">What makes Beautiful Exiles a novel when it’s based on facts? What am I missing ? Thanks</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1482314'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F36439331-beautiful-exiles">like</a></span>

